{"id":6,"ayahs":[{"number":30,"arabic":"وَإِذْ قَالَ رَبُّكَ لِلْمَلَٰٓئِكَةِ إِنِّى جَاعِلٌۭ فِى ٱلْأَرْضِ خَلِيفَةًۭ ۖ قَالُوٓا۟ أَتَجْعَلُ فِيهَا مَن يُفْسِدُ فِيهَا وَيَسْفِكُ ٱلدِّمَآءَ وَنَحْنُ نُسَبِّحُ بِحَمْدِكَ وَنُقَدِّسُ لَكَ ۖ قَالَ إِنِّىٓ أَعْلَمُ مَا لَا تَعْلَمُونَ","translation":"AND LO! Thy Sustainer said unto the angels: \"Behold, I am about to establish upon earth one who shall inherit it.\" They said: \"Wilt Thou place on it such as will spread corruption thereon and shed blood -whereas it is we who extol Thy limitless glory, and praise Thee, and hallow Thy name?\" [God] answered: \"Verily, I know that which you do not know.\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/37.mp3","surahId":2,"words":[{"id":32691,"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذْ","translation":"এবং (স্মরণ করো) যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/002_030_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32692,"position":2,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"বলেছিলেন","audioUrl":"wbw/002_030_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32693,"position":3,"arabic":"رَبُّكَ","translation":"তোমার রব","audioUrl":"wbw/002_030_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32694,"position":4,"arabic":"لِلْمَلَـٰٓئِكَةِ","translation":"ফেরেশতাদের উদ্দেশে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_030_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32695,"position":5,"arabic":"إِنِّى","translation":"''নিশ্চয়ই আমি","audioUrl":"wbw/002_030_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32696,"position":6,"arabic":"جَاعِلٌۭ","translation":"সৃষ্টিকারী","audioUrl":"wbw/002_030_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32697,"position":7,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_030_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32698,"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْضِ","translation":"পৃথিবীতর","audioUrl":"wbw/002_030_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32699,"position":9,"arabic":"خَلِيفَةًۭ ۖ","translation":"প্রতিনিধি","audioUrl":"wbw/002_030_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32701,"position":10,"arabic":"قَالُوٓا۟","translation":"তারা বলেছিলো","audioUrl":